01:27:08.556 --> 01:27:10.474
It's a political meeting!

01:27:11.643 --> 01:27:16.563
Oh, it looks like a political meeting,
but smells more like Klan to me

01:27:16.814 --> 01:27:19.983
with or without the Halloween costumes.

01:27:20.818 --> 01:27:22.319
Gentlemen.

01:27:22.487 --> 01:27:26.198
In the courts of Mississippi,
they've been reminded

01:27:26.407 --> 01:27:32.120
that they cannot turn our communities
into their communities.

01:27:32.330 --> 01:27:36.667
Communities in which Negroes
run riot, unrestrained

01:27:36.876 --> 01:27:39.211
as they do in Harlem

01:27:39.420 --> 01:27:41.088
or they do in Oakland

01:27:41.297 --> 01:27:43.340
or they do in the streets of Chicago!

01:29:04.630 --> 01:29:06.423
Can I come in?

01:29:14.932 --> 01:29:17.142
It's not good for you to be here.

01:29:17.352 --> 01:29:18.769
Why?

01:29:18.978 --> 01:29:20.562
It's ugly.

01:29:20.897 --> 01:29:23.732
This whole thing is so ugly.

01:29:24.233 --> 01:29:27.778
Do you know what it's like
to live with all this?

01:29:28.780 --> 01:29:33.867
People look at us and only see
bigots and racists.

01:29:35.578 --> 01:29:38.372
Hatred isn't something you're born with.

01:29:38.831 --> 01:29:40.791
It gets taught.

01:29:42.543 --> 01:29:46.880
At school, they said
segregation was in the Bible.

01:29:48.049 --> 01:29:52.719
Genesis 9, verse 27.

01:29:54.972 --> 01:29:57.182
At seven years of age,

01:29:57.392 --> 01:30:00.977
you get told it enough, you believe it.

01:30:01.979 --> 01:30:04.147
You believe the hatred.

01:30:05.066 --> 01:30:09.486
You live it, you breathe it.

01:30:11.072 --> 01:30:13.365
You marry it.

01:30:43.438 --> 01:30:46.215
My husband drove one of the cars
that night.

01:30:47.525 --> 01:30:50.527
That's what you wanted
to hear, isn't it?

01:30:51.529 --> 01:30:54.865
The bodies are buried
on the Roberts' Farm

01:30:55.074 --> 01:30:57.534
in an earthen dam.

01:31:15.178 --> 01:31:16.761
Sir.

01:31:29.442 --> 01:31:31.693
Take a break, Mr. Bird.

01:31:31.986 --> 01:31:34.821
Put some handkerchiefs on your faces.

01:31:52.089 --> 01:31:53.757
Make way, folks.

01:32:04.727 --> 01:32:08.271
The missing civil rights
workers were found

01:32:08.439 --> 01:32:10.106
at an undisclosed grave.

01:32:12.235 --> 01:32:16.404
Neither the FBI nor Sheriff's
Department will comment.

01:32:16.822 --> 01:32:19.533
The bodies are at Jessup County Hospital

01:32:19.742 --> 01:32:21.743
where officials refuse to comment.

01:32:21.953 --> 01:32:26.456
There is speculation
that an autopsy will be performed.

01:32:28.793 --> 01:32:30.293
Keep it open.

01:32:30.503 --> 01:32:33.547
Coming through. Open it up.

01:32:35.216 --> 01:32:37.092
Hold it back.

01:32:57.196 --> 01:33:00.156
Clinton, you got some problems at home.

01:33:00.324 --> 01:33:01.726
What do you mean?

01:33:01.826 --> 01:33:04.869
Pull your head out your ass
and get home!

01:33:05.663 --> 01:33:07.190
I, Vincent Thompson,

01:33:07.290 --> 01:33:10.917
am the cheddar cheese champion
of the world.

01:33:11.377 --> 01:33:14.671
In international competition,

01:33:14.839 --> 01:33:18.174
my cheddar won first prize
based on flavor,

01:33:18.342 --> 01:33:21.344
texture, appearance, and color.

01:33:21.554 --> 01:33:25.473
I've been a cheesemaker since I was 17.

01:33:25.683 --> 01:33:28.685
I didn't expect you home so early.

01:33:30.521 --> 01:33:32.355
Hi, Frank.

01:33:44.035 --> 01:33:46.661
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

01:33:59.216 --> 01:34:00.675
Sir.

01:34:03.512 --> 01:34:05.263
Say again.

01:34:06.891 --> 01:34:09.017
I'll be right there.

01:34:13.814 --> 01:34:15.899
- Mr. Bird.
- Yes, sir?

01:34:16.108 --> 01:34:19.027
Get five men and meet me outside.

01:34:20.613 --> 01:34:21.806
Where's Anderson?

01:34:21.906 --> 01:34:23.573
He's at the motel.

01:34:28.579 --> 01:34:29.829
Take the front door.

01:34:30.039 --> 01:34:32.540
If anyone comes in, break them down.

01:34:32.750 --> 01:34:34.250
Take the corridor.

01:34:34.460 --> 01:34:36.336
- Mr. Bird.
- Sir?

01:34:37.380 --> 01:34:41.257
Okay. Go get Anderson. Bring him here.

01:34:41.425 --> 01:34:45.095
Don't tell him anything. Get him here.

01:35:17.670 --> 01:35:19.879
Mr. Anderson, stop!

01:35:20.089 --> 01:35:21.548
- Mr. Anderson!
- Go to hell!

01:35:21.757 --> 01:35:23.717
I'm telling you to stop.

01:35:23.843 --> 01:35:25.135
We're not killers.

01:35:25.302 --> 01:35:27.455
The difference between them and us.

01:35:27.555 --> 01:35:28.972
Them and you.

01:35:29.181 --> 01:35:30.640
You're not like them.

01:35:30.808 --> 01:35:35.061
What do you care what I do to
someone hiding behind a badge?

01:35:35.271 --> 01:35:36.964
Aren't you changing the world?

01:35:37.064 --> 01:35:38.356
Yes.

01:35:38.566 --> 01:35:40.483
You're arrogant and stupid!

01:35:40.693 --> 01:35:42.219
You're changing it, too.

01:35:42.319 --> 01:35:43.945
I am right now.

01:35:44.155 --> 01:35:48.392
Don't mess this up because you're
fooling around with witnesses.

01:35:48.492 --> 01:35:49.576
You!

01:35:58.502 --> 01:36:00.795
That don't mean shit.

01:36:01.005 --> 01:36:03.506
I'll kill you if you don't listen.

01:36:03.674 --> 01:36:04.950
Fuck you.

01:36:05.050 --> 01:36:06.301
Let me go.

01:36:06.510 --> 01:36:09.345
Let me go.

01:36:09.513 --> 01:36:11.890
We'll go after them together.

01:36:12.099 --> 01:36:13.584
You wouldn't know how.

01:36:13.684 --> 01:36:15.059
You'll teach me.

01:36:15.269 --> 01:36:17.004
You don't have the guts.

01:36:17.104 --> 01:36:19.856
I have the guts and the authority.

01:36:20.065 --> 01:36:22.009
What does that mean?

01:36:22.109 --> 01:36:23.777
New rules.

01:36:23.986 --> 01:36:27.322
We nail them any way. Even your way.

01:36:27.531 --> 01:36:29.975
Is this you or someone else?

01:36:30.075 --> 01:36:31.743
Both.

01:36:32.495 --> 01:36:35.413
We do it my way with my people!

01:36:35.623 --> 01:36:37.957
Whatever it takes.

01:36:39.126 --> 01:36:40.794
Okay.

01:36:47.176 --> 01:36:48.968
Give me a minute.

01:36:57.061 --> 01:36:58.629
Would he have shot me?

01:36:58.729 --> 01:37:00.271
Yes, sir.

01:37:01.065 --> 01:37:03.733
He's a ballsy bastard, isn't he?

01:37:11.742 --> 01:37:16.814
They want me to say
that two white boys also died

01:37:16.914 --> 01:37:19.541
helping Negroes help themselves.

01:37:22.419 --> 01:37:24.128
They want me to say

01:37:24.338 --> 01:37:28.591
we mourn with the mothers
of these two white boys.

01:37:31.095 --> 01:37:33.137
But the State of Mississippi

01:37:33.347 --> 01:37:39.394
won't allow these boys to be buried
in the same cemetery as this Negro boy.

01:37:41.814 --> 01:37:46.276
I say, I have no more love to give.

01:37:46.443 --> 01:37:53.032
I have only anger in my heart today,
and I want you to be angry with me!

01:37:53.242 --> 01:37:58.913
I am sick, and I am tired,
and I want you to be sick and tired!

01:37:59.123 --> 01:38:04.544
I am sick and tired
of going to funerals of black men

01:38:04.795 --> 01:38:07.130
who've been murdered by white men.

01:38:07.298 --> 01:38:11.301
I am sick and tired of
the people of this country

01:38:11.510 --> 01:38:15.388
who continue to allow
these things to happen.

01:38:15.598 --> 01:38:20.143
What is an "unalienable right"
if you are a Negro?

01:38:20.352 --> 01:38:23.730
What does "equal treatment
under the law" mean?

01:38:23.939 --> 01:38:29.193
What does it mean
"liberty and justice for all"?

01:38:29.403 --> 01:38:34.324
Now I say to these people,
look at this young man

01:38:34.533 --> 01:38:37.619
and you'll see the face of a black man,

01:38:37.828 --> 01:38:40.663
but if you look at the blood, it's red!

01:38:40.831 --> 01:38:45.376
It is like yours! It is just like yours!

01:40:14.883 --> 01:40:15.925
You.

01:40:19.179 --> 01:40:21.806
I'm going to tell you a story.

01:40:22.933 --> 01:40:27.729
A kid named Homer Wilkes,
lives about 30 miles north of here.

01:40:28.355 --> 01:40:33.234
He'd taken his girl home
and was walking back along the road

01:40:34.069 --> 01:40:35.778
when a car pulled up.

01:40:36.447 --> 01:40:40.116
Three white boys took him for a ride.

01:40:43.287 --> 01:40:44.954
Now,

01:40:46.040 --> 01:40:48.624
he hadn't done anything

01:40:50.335 --> 01:40:51.502
except

01:40:53.464 --> 01:40:55.631
be a Negro.

01:40:58.177 --> 01:41:00.386
They took him to a shack.

01:41:01.180 --> 01:41:04.807
A shack like this one.

01:41:04.975 --> 01:41:07.310
They took out a razor blade.

01:41:08.228 --> 01:41:11.606
Regular razor blade like this one.

01:41:14.026 --> 01:41:17.195
They pulled down his pants,

01:41:19.990 --> 01:41:22.325
they spread his legs

01:41:24.286 --> 01:41:26.996
and they sliced off his scrotum.

01:41:30.125 --> 01:41:32.502
Put it in a coffee cup.

01:41:37.216 --> 01:41:42.678
Do you know how you bleed
when somebody cuts off your balls?

01:41:48.060 --> 01:41:49.894
Homer looked like

01:41:50.104 --> 01:41:53.564
he'd been dipped in blood
up to his waist.

01:41:53.816 --> 01:41:57.193
He was barely alive when
he got to the hospital.

01:41:57.361 --> 01:41:59.821
He can hardly walk now.

01:42:09.873 --> 01:42:12.917
Mayor, we know you know who was there

01:42:13.127 --> 01:42:16.045
when those civil rights boys was killed.

01:42:16.380 --> 01:42:19.257
You know who pulled the trigger.

01:42:25.097 --> 01:42:27.598
You want to say something to me?

01:42:34.148 --> 01:42:35.731
Okay.

01:42:40.821 --> 01:42:42.890
Is he with the Bureau?

01:42:42.990 --> 01:42:45.074
He's a specialist.

01:42:45.242 --> 01:42:46.769
The mayor won't talk?

01:42:46.869 --> 01:42:48.327
They'd kill him.

01:42:48.537 --> 01:42:50.773
What do you have?

01:42:50.873 --> 01:42:53.207
Three cars, seven men involved.

01:42:53.417 --> 01:42:54.651
Pell and Bailey killed them.

01:42:54.751 --> 01:42:55.918
Stuckey?

01:42:56.086 --> 01:42:59.505
He's too smart to be there. Pell did it.

01:42:59.798 --> 01:43:00.908
And Townley?

01:43:01.008 --> 01:43:02.091
It was his idea.

01:43:02.259 --> 01:43:04.594
Grand Dragons don't get dirty.

01:43:04.803 --> 01:43:08.931
The whole thing? Bullet by bullet.

01:43:09.600 --> 01:43:11.309
Are you interested

01:43:11.518 --> 01:43:16.272
in words like coercion
or hearsay or duress?

01:43:16.481 --> 01:43:18.842
This is no good in court.

01:43:18.942 --> 01:43:20.735
We're not in court.

01:43:20.944 --> 01:43:24.822
We won't get them on murder.
That's a state charge.

01:43:25.032 --> 01:43:26.616
They won't prosecute.

01:43:26.783 --> 01:43:29.952
We've got to get them in Federal Court.

01:43:30.162 --> 01:43:31.522
Violation of civil rights!

01:43:31.622 --> 01:43:34.123
You're violating rights!

01:43:34.291 --> 01:43:36.110
Don't put me on your perch!

01:43:36.210 --> 01:43:38.127
Don't drag me in your gutter!

01:43:38.295 --> 01:43:41.130
These people crawled out of the sewer!

01:43:41.340 --> 01:43:44.008
Maybe the gutter's where we should be!

01:43:49.640 --> 01:43:51.349
Thank you.

01:44:15.332 --> 01:44:17.416
This better be important.

01:44:25.842 --> 01:44:27.718
Who called this meeting?

01:44:31.056 --> 01:44:32.515
We thought you did.

01:44:32.683 --> 01:44:34.767
Of this group? Are you stupid?

01:44:34.977 --> 01:44:36.811
You didn't call this?

01:44:37.020 --> 01:44:38.422
Who the fuck did?

01:44:38.522 --> 01:44:39.897
Shut up!

01:44:40.107 --> 01:44:41.466
Wait!

01:44:41.566 --> 01:44:43.484
Is this a bullshit setup?

01:44:43.694 --> 01:44:45.736
Ray, you didn't call this?

01:44:45.946 --> 01:44:49.532
I got a note from you and Clinton.

01:44:49.992 --> 01:44:51.325
Lester, shut up!

01:44:53.912 --> 01:44:58.207
Now, we're all gonna
walk straight out of here

01:44:58.417 --> 01:45:00.418
and say nothing.

01:45:00.627 --> 01:45:02.878
That means nothing, Lester.

01:45:03.088 --> 01:45:04.740
You speak, you're dead.

01:45:04.840 --> 01:45:06.424
Shut up.

01:45:07.259 --> 01:45:09.010
Hey, Clinton.

01:45:12.639 --> 01:45:14.390
Clinton?

01:45:17.853 --> 01:45:21.605
The rattlesnakes are starting
to commit suicide.

01:45:49.509 --> 01:45:51.093
Hi, Lester.

01:45:56.516 --> 01:45:58.517
We'll give you that ride home.

01:46:00.270 --> 01:46:01.672
What?

01:46:01.772 --> 01:46:03.105
I know you said 4:30.

01:46:03.273 --> 01:46:05.232
We're running late.

01:46:05.942 --> 01:46:07.761
I'll meet you in the car.

01:46:07.861 --> 01:46:09.653
You're cracked.

01:46:10.947 --> 01:46:13.100
You have change for a $20?

01:46:13.200 --> 01:46:15.618
Sure.

01:46:21.416 --> 01:46:23.334
Get in the car, Lester.

01:46:23.543 --> 01:46:27.463
Or it'll be hard picking your
nose once I shut this drawer.

01:46:31.259 --> 01:46:35.763
You could make it easier on yourself
by going on the record.

01:46:35.972 --> 01:46:38.265
I ain't got nothing to say.

01:46:38.475 --> 01:46:41.394
You're barking up
the wrong tree, mister.

01:46:42.020 --> 01:46:44.105
I've got to tell you something.

01:46:44.314 --> 01:46:48.192
We've got you cold. Your buddies talked.

01:46:49.611 --> 01:46:51.320
You're lying.

01:46:56.493 --> 01:46:58.202
You're in a lot of trouble.

01:46:58.412 --> 01:47:02.581
You drove the second vehicle,
the green truck.

01:47:02.791 --> 01:47:04.917
Your buddy... Refresh my memory.

01:47:05.127 --> 01:47:08.170
"Lester dragged the Negro from the car

01:47:08.338 --> 01:47:09.839
"and shot him."

01:47:10.048 --> 01:47:11.575
That's a lie!

01:47:11.675 --> 01:47:13.509
It's true. What else, Mr. Bird?

01:47:13.677 --> 01:47:18.556
He said, "They only left me a nigger,
but at least I shot one."

01:47:21.101 --> 01:47:24.478
I didn't kill him.
I shot him in the ass.

01:47:24.688 --> 01:47:28.315
He was already dead when
you put a slug in him.

01:47:28.525 --> 01:47:32.820
Your buddy tells it
that you killed the kid.

01:47:33.029 --> 01:47:35.239
Go on the record for us

01:47:35.449 --> 01:47:39.160
or it's your ass,
not just a black kid's!

01:47:53.216 --> 01:47:55.176
Think about it, Lester.

01:47:55.594 --> 01:47:57.052
Come on out of there.

01:47:58.805 --> 01:48:00.556
Come on out.

01:48:44.518 --> 01:48:46.602
This is tricky.

01:48:47.687 --> 01:48:50.940
They make it look so easy, don't they?

01:48:51.733 --> 01:48:54.276
I got a question for you, Clinton.

01:48:55.445 --> 01:48:58.447
You don't mind if I call you Clinton?

01:48:58.657 --> 01:49:01.367
I feel like I know you so well.

01:49:03.620 --> 01:49:07.164
The way we have it,
on the night of the murders,

01:49:07.374 --> 01:49:11.293
you made a speech as you
buried the kids in the dam.

01:49:11.461 --> 01:49:15.381
How does Lester tell it?
"Mississippi would be proud.

01:49:15.590 --> 01:49:18.384
"You've struck a blow
for the white man."

01:49:18.593 --> 01:49:21.220
Is that what you said?

01:49:22.055 --> 01:49:26.517
Is that what you said?
It must have been you.

01:49:26.726 --> 01:49:31.981
Clayton Townley and Ray Stuckey
were too smart to be there.

01:49:32.190 --> 01:49:36.193
You didn't think anyone would remember.

01:49:36.987 --> 01:49:40.056
But old Lester, he got a good memory.

01:49:43.994 --> 01:49:48.163
I'm sorry. I haven't done this
for a long time.

01:49:48.373 --> 01:49:49.983
Did you make a speech

01:49:50.083 --> 01:49:53.603
the night you beat up your wife?

01:49:53.703 --> 01:49:55.529
Did you?

01:49:56.298 --> 01:49:59.117
Did you strike a blow
for the white man that night?

01:50:03.597 --> 01:50:06.390
You got a stupid smile. You know that?

01:50:06.600 --> 01:50:08.434
Can you see it?

01:50:10.645 --> 01:50:15.524
Did you smile when the bulldozer
ran over the body? Did you?

01:50:19.237 --> 01:50:22.865
Did you smile when
the bodies were covered over?

01:50:23.366 --> 01:50:25.826
Get up here. Come on!

01:50:26.036 --> 01:50:30.539
Did you smile that same stupid smile?
Did you?

01:50:36.087 --> 01:50:39.340
Did you smile, Pell? Did you smile?

01:50:47.891 --> 01:50:50.309
Make no mistake, Deputy.

01:50:50.518 --> 01:50:52.629
I'll cut your head off

01:50:52.729 --> 01:50:55.773
and not give a shit how it
reads in the report.

01:51:18.588 --> 01:51:21.757
One more bite. One more bite.

01:51:21.925 --> 01:51:24.718
One more bite, darling. One more bite.

01:51:41.444 --> 01:51:44.180
Shit, Lester! What is going on?

01:51:44.280 --> 01:51:47.741
Get in the bedroom and lock the door!

01:51:47.867 --> 01:51:50.035
Stay away from the windows!

01:53:06.696 --> 01:53:10.115
Please! Please! I didn't say a thing!

01:53:10.325 --> 01:53:13.118
It's a setup! I didn't say nothing!

01:53:14.496 --> 01:53:17.623
Nothing! I didn't say nothing!

01:53:17.832 --> 01:53:19.374
I didn't say nothing!

01:53:26.800 --> 01:53:28.634
I didn't say nothing!

01:53:49.072 --> 01:53:52.267
You're lucky we been watching your ass.

01:53:55.119 --> 01:53:59.623
If you go on the record,
we'll give you protection.

01:53:59.833 --> 01:54:00.833
If not...

01:54:01.042 --> 01:54:04.753
If not, they're gonna kill you anyway.

01:54:04.963 --> 01:54:08.799
Oh! You need a toilet, Lester.

01:54:33.032 --> 01:54:35.409
Really had him going.

01:55:19.537 --> 01:55:22.372
We'll take care of the check.

01:55:46.731 --> 01:55:49.608
Well, I suppose I'll be back for supper.

01:57:16.946 --> 01:57:18.613
Why did he do it?

01:57:19.282 --> 01:57:22.034
He wasn't even in on it.

01:57:22.243 --> 01:57:23.952
He wasn't even Klan.

01:57:24.495 --> 01:57:27.456
Mr. Bird, he was guilty.

01:57:27.790 --> 01:57:31.877
Anyone's guilty who watches this
happen and pretends it isn't.

01:57:32.879 --> 01:57:36.423
No, he was guilty, all right.

01:57:36.841 --> 01:57:40.260
As guilty as the ones
who pulled the trigger.

01:57:42.555 --> 01:57:44.014
Maybe we all are.

01:58:38.361 --> 01:58:39.361
Hello?

01:58:41.405 --> 01:58:42.739
Yeah.

01:58:49.539 --> 01:58:54.042
I just missed you at the hospital.
They said you'd gone home.

01:58:55.002 --> 01:58:57.087
What's left of it.

01:58:58.548 --> 01:59:00.048
I'm real sorry.

01:59:00.508 --> 01:59:02.384
So am I.

01:59:03.177 --> 01:59:04.662
What are you gonna do?

01:59:04.762 --> 01:59:06.429
I don't know.

